<li>Grothendieck category <sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Grothendieck_inequality" title="Grothendieck inequality">Grothendieck inequality</a> or <a href="/wiki/Grothendieck_constant" title="Grothendieck constant" class="mw-redirect">Grothendieck constant</a></li>
